392
00:27:19,581 --> 00:27:22,081
我慢、我慢。
Patience, patience.

393
00:27:22,081 --> 00:27:25,581
メル様の頼みならしょうがないなあ。
If it's Mel-sama's request, I guess I have no choice.

394
00:27:26,081 --> 00:27:29,081
ちょっと元戻しとこ。
I'll put it back for a bit.

395
00:27:29,081 --> 00:27:33,081
