Mel would like to challenge you to a battle,

396
00:27:34,081 --> 00:27:35,581
いいかな？
is that okay?

397
00:27:36,081 --> 00:27:37,581
もちろん！
Of course!

398
00:27:38,081 --> 00:27:43,081
まあメル様の勝負なら楽勝で勝っちゃうと思うんでね。
Well, if it's a battle against Mel-sama, I think I'll win easily.

399
00:27:44,081 --> 00:27:48,081
ん、じゃあ勝負のルール説明をするね。
Alright, then I'll explain the rules of the battle.

400
00:27:49,081 --> 00:27:53,081
今から3つのシチュエーションを準備します。
I've prepared three situations.

401
00:27:54,081 --> 00:27:54,881
はい。
Yes.

402
00:27:54,881 --> 00:27:57,581
